{"tid":684662,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[無劇透]黑鏡第四季第2集","createTime":"2018-05-30T17:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T12:58:25.000Z","uid":5375,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f2cd040878453bbf6f6914550f2a4b3849ef85","tid":684662,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"女主角叫sarah<br />\n導演Jodie Foster<br />\n<br />\n1988年Jodie Foster憑the accused獲61屆奧斯卡影后<br />\nthe accused主角正是sarah<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然呢集麻麻地，隻科技好老套，<br />\n但個主題非常有意義，面對子女既成長，家長可以點樣健康地監護，<br />\n男又好女又好，幾多人係成長過程中只因一瞬間既迷途，就誤了一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49ef7b9f6fc75e312f29a87e3f8b86273f09181","tid":684662,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00ca512ed5f89e51b36869d49991f8c9e572e3c2","tid":684662,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"唔記得咗邊集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無圖"},{"pid":"7215dbc903dafaba7dd01ae9112d9cece8c31c25","tid":684662,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:43:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩母女都係臭雞<br />\n抵撚死</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef54edcba359f65e9d5dc912c7d79fda939c7b41","tid":684662,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00ca512ed5f89e51b36869d49991f8c9e572e3c2","tid":684662,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"唔記得咗邊集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T17:52:07.000Z","msg":"兩母女，個女細個被老母裝左個監護裝置入腦"},{"pid":"a2759d0402bb62e267c756f6110341f6a14c600f","tid":684662,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc